summary: “Director Komiya A meerkat regarded as irritating and a sissy. He seems to be miserable. He is highly upward-intentioned, and is...
body:
“Director Komiya

A meerkat regarded as irritating and a sissy. He seems to be miserable. He is highly upward-intentioned, and is absolutely obedient to those in higher positions due to his desire to rise in the ranks. Because of this, he is desperate enough to take credit for his subordinates’ work. When things get inconvenient, he becomes aggressive with his subordinates. “

I tried to do my own translation of Komiya’s bio and I thought it gave a good look into this guy’s character. 

I don’t speak Japanese, I just did what I could :> But I found it interesting that it makes a point to say that he’s pretty much miserable and a coward, and only sucks up to Ton because he’s so desperate to climb the ladder?  I mean, as a Komiya fan, I think it’s interesting.

 if they could develop some of this characterization into his Netflix character I’d love that.
